thread.title: BRIEF-Nilorngruppen Q4 Order Intake Up At SEK ‍184​ Million

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Nilorngruppen Q4 Order Intake Up At SEK ‍184​ Million
text:
Feb 16 (Reuters) - NILORNGRUPPEN AB:
* Q4 ORDER INTAKE SEK ‍184​ MILLION VERSUS SEK 169 MILLION YEAR AGO
* Q4 REVENUE SEK ‍191​ MILLION VERSUS SEK 174 MILLION YEAR AGO
* ‍TO PROPOSE TO ANNUAL GENERAL MEETING A DIVIDEND OF 4.00 (3.60) PER SHARE​
* Q4 OPERATING PROFIT SEK 26.3 MILLION VERSUS SEK 22.1 MILLION YEAR AGO
* Q4 PROFIT FOR PERIOD AMOUNTED TO MSEK 22.1 (15.4) Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
